#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:5
msgid "Writing Guidelines"
msgstr "Smernice za pisanje"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:12
msgid ""
"In general, when creating reST documentation for the QGIS project, please "
"follow the `Python documentation style guidelines "
"<https://devguide.python.org/documenting/>`_. For convenience, we provide a "
"set of general rules we rely on for writing QGIS documentation below."
msgstr ""
"Uopšteno, pri pravljenju reST dokumentacije za QGIS projekat, pratite "
"`smernice za stil Python dokumentacije "
"<https://devguide.python.org/documenting/>`_. Radi praktičnosti, ispod "
"pružamo skup opštih pravila na koja se oslanjamo pri pisanju QGIS "
"dokumentacije."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:19
msgid "Writing Documentation"
msgstr "Pisanje dokumentacije"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:22
msgid "Headlines"
msgstr "Naslovi"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:24
msgid "To each webpage of the documentation corresponds a ``.rst`` file."
msgstr "Svakoj veb stranici dokumentacije odgovara ``.rst`` datoteka."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:26
msgid ""
"Sections used to structure the text are identified through their title which"
" is underlined (and overlined for the first level). Same level titles must "
"use same character for underline adornment. Precede section titles with a "
"blank line. In QGIS Documentation, you should use following styles for "
"chapter, section, subsection and minisec."
msgstr ""
"Odeljci koji se koriste za strukturiranje teksta prepoznaju se po svom "
"naslovu koji je podvučen (a za prvi nivo i nadvučen). Naslovi istog nivoa "
"moraju koristiti isti znak za ukras podvlačenja. Naslovima odeljaka prethodi"
" prazan red. U QGIS dokumentaciji treba da koristite sledeće stilove za "
"poglavlje, odeljak, pododeljak i minisec."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:52
msgid "Lists"
msgstr "Liste"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:54
msgid ""
"Lists are useful for structuring the text.  Here are some simple rules "
"common to all lists:"
msgstr ""
"Liste su korisne za strukturiranje teksta. Evo nekih jednostavnih pravila "
"zajedničkih svim listama:"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:57
msgid "Start all list items with a capital letter"
msgstr "Sve stavke liste počinjite velikim slovom"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:59
msgid ""
"Do not use punctuation after list items that only contain a single simple "
"sentence"
msgstr ""
"Ne koristite interpunkciju posle stavki liste koje sadrže samo jednu "
"jednostavnu rečenicu"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:62
msgid ""
"Use period ( ``.`` ) as punctuation for list items that consist of several "
"sentences or a single compound sentence"
msgstr ""
"Koristite tačku ( ``.`` ) kao interpunkciju za stavke liste koje se sastoje "
"od više rečenica ili jedne složene rečenice"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:66
msgid "Indentation"
msgstr "Uvlačenje"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:68
msgid ""
"Indentation in reStructuredText should be aligned with the list or markup "
"*marker*. It is also possible to create block quotes with indentation. See "
"the `Specification "
"<https://docutils.sourceforge.io/docs/ref/rst/restructuredtext.html#indentation>`__"
msgstr ""
"Uvlačenje u reStructuredText-u treba poravnati sa *oznakom* liste ili "
"markupa. Takođe je moguće praviti blok citate uvlačenjem. Pogledajte "
"`Specifikaciju "
"<https://docutils.sourceforge.io/docs/ref/rst/restructuredtext.html#indentation>`__"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:92
msgid "Inline Tags"
msgstr "Ugrađene oznake"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:94
msgid "You can use tags to emphasize items."
msgstr "Oznake možete koristiti za isticanje stavki."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:96
msgid ""
"**Menu GUI**: to mark a complete sequence of menu selections, including "
"selecting submenus and choosing a specific operation, or any subsequence of "
"such a sequence."
msgstr ""
"**GUI menija**: za označavanje potpune sekvence izbora u meniju, uključujući"
" izbor podmenija i konkretne operacije, ili bilo koje podsekvence takve "
"sekvence."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:104
msgid ""
"**Dialogs and Tab titles**: Labels presented as part of an interactive user "
"interface including window titles, tab titles, button and option labels."
msgstr ""
"**Naslovi dijaloga i kartica**: Natpisi predstavljeni kao deo interaktivnog "
"korisničkog interfejsa, uključujući naslove prozora, naslove kartica, "
"natpise dugmadi i opcija."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:111
msgid "**Filenames and directories**"
msgstr "**Nazivi datoteka i direktorijuma**"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:117
msgid "**Icons with popup text**"
msgstr "**Ikone sa iskačućim tekstom**"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:123
msgid "(see `image`_ below)."
msgstr "(pogledajte `image`_ ispod)."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:125
msgid "**Keyboard shortcuts**"
msgstr "**Prečice na tastaturi**"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:131
msgid "will show :kbd:`Ctrl+B`"
msgstr "prikazaće :kbd:`Ctrl+B`"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:133
msgid ""
"When describing keyboard shortcuts, the following conventions should be "
"used:"
msgstr ""
"Pri opisivanju prečica na tastaturi treba koristiti sledeće konvencije:"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:136
msgid "Letter keys are displayed using uppercase: :kbd:`S`"
msgstr "Slovni tasteri se prikazuju velikim slovima: :kbd:`S`"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:137
msgid "Special keys are displayed with an uppercase first letter: :kbd:`Esc`"
msgstr "Specijalni tasteri se prikazuju sa velikim prvim slovom: :kbd:`Esc`"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:138
msgid ""
"Key combinations are displayed with a ``+`` sign between keys, without "
"spaces: :kbd:`Shift+R`"
msgstr ""
"Kombinacije tastera se prikazuju sa znakom ``+`` između tastera, bez "
"razmaka: :kbd:`Shift+R`"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:141
msgid "**User text**"
msgstr "**Korisnički tekst**"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:147
msgid "**Layers, databases, tables or columns names**"
msgstr "**Nazivi slojeva, baza podataka, tabela ili kolona**"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:149
msgid ""
"When referring to layers, databases, tables or columns, format as inline "
"code:"
msgstr ""
"Pri upućivanju na slojeve, baze podataka, tabele ili kolone, formatirajte "
"kao ugrađeni kôd:"

