"reference:"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:211
msgid "which returns:"
msgstr "što vraća:"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:213
msgid "see :ref:`Label and reference <my_anchor>` for more information."
msgstr "pogledajte :ref:`Natpis i referenca <my_anchor>` za više informacija."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:219
