msgstr "što vraća"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:238
msgid "Icon substitution"
msgstr "Zamena ikonom"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:240
msgid ""
"You can add an image inside a text paragraph (e.g., as a tool icon). To do "
"so, you first need to create an alias (also named substitution), which is a "
"reference name used to display the icon. To ensure consistency across the "
"documents and help in the use of the icons, we maintain a list in the "
":file:`substitutions.txt` file at the root of this repository. Find more "
"details in the :ref:`substitutions` chapter."
msgstr ""
"Sliku možete dodati unutar tekstualnog pasusa (npr. kao ikonu alatke). Da "
"biste to uradili, prvo morate napraviti alijas (nazvan i zamena), što je "
"referentni naziv koji se koristi za prikaz ikone. Radi obezbeđivanja "
"doslednosti u dokumentima i pomoći pri korišćenju ikona, održavamo listu u "
"datoteci :file:`substitutions.txt` u korenu ovog repozitorijuma. Više "
"detalja pronađite u poglavlju :ref:`substitutions`."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:247
msgid "Using an icon substitution is usually achieved through these steps:"
msgstr "Korišćenje zamene ikonom obično se postiže kroz ove korake:"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:249
msgid ""
"Add the icon substitution in the :file:`substitutions.txt` file as below. If"
" a substitution already exists for the icon you want to use, then skip this "
"step."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte zamenu ikonom u datoteku :file:`substitutions.txt` kao ispod. Ako "
"zamena za ikonu koju želite da koristite već postoji, preskočite ovaj korak."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:257
msgid "Call it in your paragraph:"
msgstr "Pozovite je u svom pasusu:"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:263
msgid ""
"Add (again) the icon substitution at the end of the file you are modifying. "
"This helps connecting the replacement text with the actual image, and can be"
" done by copy-pasting it from :file:`substitutions.txt` or by executing the "
":file:`scripts/find_set_subst.py` script."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte (ponovo) zamenu ikonom na kraju datoteke koju menjate. Ovo pomaže u "
"povezivanju teksta zamene sa stvarnom slikom, a može se uraditi kopiranjem "
"iz :file:`substitutions.txt` ili izvršavanjem skripte "
":file:`scripts/find_set_subst.py`."

