msgid "see :numref:`figure_logo`"
msgstr "pogledajte :numref:`figure_logo`"

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:318
msgid "This is the preferred way of referencing figures."
msgstr "Ovo je preferirani način upućivanja na slike."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:322
msgid "For ``:numref:`` to work, the figure **must have a caption**."
msgstr "Da bi ``:numref:`` radilo, slika **mora imati natpis**."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:324
