#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:359
msgid ""
"Tables should have a caption. You can use an explicit reST `\"table\" "
"directive "
"<https://docutils.sourceforge.io/docs/ref/rst/directives.html#table>`_ to "
"add a caption to `simple tables "
"<https://docutils.sourceforge.io/docs/ref/rst/restructuredtext.html#simple-"
"tables>`_ or `grid tables "
"<https://docutils.sourceforge.io/docs/ref/rst/restructuredtext.html#grid-"
"tables>`_. Add the caption on the same line as the directive and indent the "
"table at least one space."
msgstr ""
"Tabele treba da imaju natpis. Možete koristiti eksplicitnu reST direktivu "
"`„table“ "
"<https://docutils.sourceforge.io/docs/ref/rst/directives.html#table>`_ da "
"biste dodali natpis `jednostavnim tabelama "
"<https://docutils.sourceforge.io/docs/ref/rst/restructuredtext.html#simple-"
"tables>`_ ili `tabelama sa mrežom "
"<https://docutils.sourceforge.io/docs/ref/rst/restructuredtext.html#grid-"
"tables>`_. Dodajte natpis u istom redu kao direktivu i uvucite tabelu bar "
"jedan razmak."

#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:365
msgid ""
"You can also add a `hyperlink target "
"<https://docutils.sourceforge.io/docs/ref/rst/restructuredtext.html#hyperlink-"
"targets>`_ before a table in order to reference it elsewhere.  To avoid "
"conflicts with other references, always begin hyperlink targets with "
"``_table_`` and use terms relevant to the table caption."
msgstr ""
"Takođe možete dodati `cilj hiperlinka "
"<https://docutils.sourceforge.io/docs/ref/rst/restructuredtext.html#hyperlink-"
"targets>`_ pre tabele da biste je negde drugde referencirali. Da biste "
"izbegli sukobe sa drugim referencama, ciljeve hiperlinka uvek počinjite sa "
"``_table_`` i koristite termine relevantne za natpis tabele."

